		Acceptance:  "1. TestHookSplit covers split\n2. cd cli && go test ./internal/agent/... green",
		Description: "PROBLEM\nToo broad.\n\nROOT CAUSE\ncli/internal/agent/foo.go:42 does too much.\n",
